high_descs: Walk forward to the wall, turn right and walk to the corner by the bed.  Turn right at the bed.
Close the lap top on the bed.  Pick up the lap top.
Turn right and walk to the desk across the room.
Put the lap top down on the desk.
Turn left and walk to the window.  Turn left at the window and walk to the side of the bed.
Pick up the lap top on the bed next to the wall by the blue pillow.
Turn to the left and walk to the door and turn left.  Walk to the desk.
Put the lap top down to the right of the first lap top on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move two lap tops from the bed to the desk.

high_descs: Walk forward to the bookcase and take a right and walk to the foot of the bed and turn right to face the bed.
Close the laptop closest to you and pick it up.
Turn right and walk until you reach the desk.
Put the laptop on the desk to the upper right from the chair.
Turn right for two steps, turn left for one step and turn right and walk to the window and turn left to the bed and stop.
Pick up the laptop behind the pillow on the bed, near the wall.
Turn left and walk to the door, turn right and walk to the desk.
Put the laptop on the desk to the right of the laptop already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two closed laptops from the bed to the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the end of the bed
Grab the laptop off of the bed
Turn right and go to the desk
Put the laptop on the desk
Turn around and go to the bed
Grab a laptop off of the bed
Turn around and go to the desk
Put the laptop on the desk to the right of the other laptop
anns.task_desc: Putting two laptops on the desk
